This repository comprises the following projects:
 
* TASK 1: Chatbot with Rule-Based Responses: A simple chatbot implemented in chattie_gui.py, which responds to user inputs based on predefined rules defined within the code.
* TASK 2: Tic-Tac-Toe AI: An artificial intelligence agent implemented in tictactoe_gui.py, designed to play the classic game of Tic-Tac-Toe against a human player. The AI utilizes the minimax algorithm without alpha-beta pruning, offering the option for the AI player to be unbeatable or random.
